name: FUKU
description: The project is about FUKU, the name of the new dog, which is a shiba inu of Atsuko Sato. She was the owner of Kabusu the famous face of Doge. Fuku is the new dog she has adopted after kabuso passed away. Being the famous owner of kabuso (doge) FUKU is still a puppy and can be a captivating symbol for blockchain memes. As the next generation of Shiba cuteness, Fuku is ready to step into the spotlight
